{
  "stem": "11882.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had been in his-- in his hands, and now here were these people who supposedly had caused all this trouble.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Well, they talk about-- nobody can count it-- 50 million dead of the war dead.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And everybody was watching Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And Nuremberg was a mess.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the heroic US Army really took care of everybody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The first winter was very cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Somehow the coal supplies didn't come through, so everybody wore the best, biggest coats and sweaters they had.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the little French girls who had been in the resistance-- the French men, too, I suppose, but I noticed the French girls-- they put on everything they had.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They were so cold with their resistance life-- came into Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And everybody pitched in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There was a tremendous spirit of work, and the work was tremendously diversified because these endless documents were funneling into Nuremberg from-- from army cars all over Europe, were bringing in, from Paris, especially.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Hitler in the last days-- I always say Hitler, he didn't probably know what was going on-- had carried great loads of documents, truckloads of documents, out to Paris to store.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was getting so bombed out in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And there was a great spirit of cooperation, and in a sense, everybody, including, strangely enough, as they assemble them-- the defendants-- was in the German population-- was in some way so relieved that the war was over.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they were all talkative.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They talked about their crimes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They talked about Hitler, himself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There was no effort.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was just a people who had been pulled out of a shock situation, the war, and didn't know when it would end, and it had ended.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, we were doing the translation, as I said.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never certainly even tried out for the interpreting.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
